A3: (for i holds ((1 <= i & i <= n) implies (( ( A * ( SwapDiagonal (K,n,j0) ) ) * (i,j0) ) = ( A * (i,1) ) & ( ( A * ( SwapDiagonal (K,n,j0) ) ) * (i,1) ) = ( A * (i,j0) ))))
proof
let i;
assume A4: (1 <= i & i <= n);
then A5: 1 <= n by XXREAL_0:2;
then A6: [ i,1 ] in ( Indices A ) by A4,MATRIX_1:37;
[ j0,i ] in ( Indices ( ( SwapDiagonal (K,n,j0) ) * ( A @ ) ) ) by A1,A4,MATRIX_1:37;
hence ( ( A * ( SwapDiagonal (K,n,j0) ) ) * (i,j0) ) = ( ( ( SwapDiagonal (K,n,j0) ) * ( A @ ) ) * (j0,i) ) by A2,MATRIX_1:def 6
.= ( ( A @ ) * (1,i) ) by A1,A4,CKB55:1
.= ( A * (i,1) ) by A6,MATRIX_1:def 6;
A7: [ i,j0 ] in ( Indices A ) by A1,A4,MATRIX_1:37;
[ 1,i ] in ( Indices ( ( SwapDiagonal (K,n,j0) ) * ( A @ ) ) ) by A4,A5,MATRIX_1:37;
hence ( ( A * ( SwapDiagonal (K,n,j0) ) ) * (i,1) ) = ( ( ( SwapDiagonal (K,n,j0) ) * ( A @ ) ) * (1,i) ) by A2,MATRIX_1:def 6
.= ( ( A @ ) * (j0,i) ) by A1,A4,CKB55:1
.= ( A * (i,j0) ) by A7,MATRIX_1:def 6;
end;
(for i holds (for j holds ((((((j <> 1 & j <> j0) & 1 <= i) & i <= n) & 1 <= j) & j <= n) implies ( ( A * ( SwapDiagonal (K,n,j0) ) ) * (i,j) ) = ( A * (i,j) ))))
